  <entry>
    <title>十六进制字符串与十六进制整形之间的转换</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2021/05/18/%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AD%E8%BF%9B%E5%88%B6%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E4%B8%8E%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AD%E8%BF%9B%E5%88%B6%E6%95%B4%E5%BD%A2%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E8%BD%AC%E6%8D%A2/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2021/05/18/%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AD%E8%BF%9B%E5%88%B6%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E4%B8%8E%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AD%E8%BF%9B%E5%88%B6%E6%95%B4%E5%BD%A2%E4%B9%8B%E9%97%B4%E7%9A%84%E8%BD%AC%E6%8D%A2/</id>
    <published>2021-05-18T08:14:28.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-05-20T08:34:48.710Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h5 id="在开始之前先谈谈标题"><a href="#在开始之前先谈谈标题" class="headerlink" title="在开始之前先谈谈标题."></a>在开始之前先谈谈标题.</h5><p>解释什么是十六进制字符串?<br>进制是计数方式,利用这方式，可以使用有限的符号来表示所有的数值。<br>我们知道,在强类型的计算机语言里,数字和字符串,是两种类型,但可不是风马牛不相及.后续我们慢慢道来,是怎么相及的.<br>也就是说十六进制字符串表示的是一个数,但是呢.这个数是用十六进制这种进制(计数方式)来表示的.</p><p>如何把这个“字符串格式的数”convert 一下. 变成一个数字类型的数.<br>常见的把它变成我们常见的“十进制类型”的数,还有一种是把它转换成“十六进制类型的数”.<br>本质上这是一种类型转换&amp;保留原来的十六进制.</p><h5 id="给整形变量赋值-十六进制-十进制-八进制-二进制"><a href="#给整形变量赋值-十六进制-十进制-八进制-二进制" class="headerlink" title="给整形变量赋值(十六进制,十进制,八进制,二进制):"></a>给整形变量赋值(十六进制,十进制,八进制,二进制):</h5><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> bInt = <span class="number">0b101</span>;   <span class="comment">//二进制数字</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> oInt = <span class="number">0456</span>;   <span class="comment">//八进制数字</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> dInt = <span class="number">567890</span>; <span class="comment">//十进制数字</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> hexInt = <span class="number">0X234FF</span>;<span class="comment">// 十六进制数字</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;八进制:bInt = %o,oInt = %o, dInt = %o,hexInt = %o\n&quot;</span>, bInt, oInt, dInt,hexInt);  <span class="comment">//以八进制形似输出</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;十进制:bInt = %d,oInt = %d,dInt = %d,hexInt = %d\n&quot;</span>,bInt,oInt,dInt,hexInt);  <span class="comment">//以十进制形式输出</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;十六进制:bInt = %x,oInt = %x, dInt = %x,hexInt = %x\n&quot;</span>,bInt,oInt,dInt,hexInt);  <span class="comment">//以十六进制形式输出（字母小写）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;十六进制:bInt = %X,oInt = %X,dInt = %X,hexInt = %X\n&quot;</span>,bInt,oInt,dInt,hexInt);  <span class="comment">//以十六进制形式输出（字母大写）</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>OK! 下面我们分别的针对这两种情况,来讨论.</p><h6 id="1-十六进制字符串-转换为-十进制数字"><a href="#1-十六进制字符串-转换为-十进制数字" class="headerlink" title="1.十六进制字符串 转换为 十进制数字"></a>1.十六进制字符串 转换为 十进制数字</h6><figure class="highlight objectivec"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> outVal;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">NSScanner</span>* scanner = [<span class="built_in">NSScanner</span> scannerWithString:<span class="string">@&quot;0x01FFFFAB&quot;</span>];</span><br><span class="line">[scanner scanHexInt:&amp;outVal];</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">NSLog</span>(<span class="string">@&quot;outVal formated with decimal is  %d&quot;</span>,outVal);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">NSLog</span>(<span class="string">@&quot;outVal formated with hex is  %x&quot;</span>,outVal);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>到达罗马的途径有很多种,这只是一种简单有效的方法.</p></blockquote><h6 id="2-十六进制字符串-转换为-十六进制数字"><a href="#2-十六进制字符串-转换为-十六进制数字" class="headerlink" title="2.十六进制字符串 转换为 十六进制数字"></a>2.十六进制字符串 转换为 十六进制数字</h6><p>先不要思考为什么要么做. 但是这么做是有意义的,计算机语言里十六进制的字符串,虽然它表示的是一个数字,但是它的类型还是字符串.我们要把字符串转换成数字类型.</p><p>懵了?<br>别懵,这个不难理解.比如说:int a = 1000,变量a的值是1000,变量a的类型是整形.再看另一个:String a = “1000”,这里a变量的值也是“1000”,a变量的类型是String类型.可能你看起来,区别不大,事实上,对计算机语言来说,区别大了.<br>到底有什么区别呢?<br>有空再聊这一块.记着这两种值都是1000,但是类型不一样,对计算机来说,他们区别大了.所以我们要转换.</p><p><strong>既然对计算机来说,区别大了,那么各程序设计语言肯定回提供一些方法或者函数来供我们调用来去完成这个convert</strong><br>下面是常见C的convert方法.</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> value;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="built_in">sscanf</span>([str UTF8String], <span class="string">&quot;%x&quot;</span>, &amp;value) == <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    NSLog(@<span class="string">&quot;Convert Success value is %x&quot;</span>,value);</span><br><span class="line">    NSLog(@<span class="string">&quot;Convert Success value is d %d&quot;</span>,value);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    NSLog(@<span class="string">&quot;Convert Fail value is fail %x&quot;</span>,value);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>既然objective c和c可以混编调用,我们也可以这样来实现转换十六进制字符串到十进制数.</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> value;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="built_in">sscanf</span>([str UTF8String], <span class="string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>, &amp;value) == <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    NSLog(@<span class="string">&quot;Convert Success value is %x&quot;</span>,value);</span><br><span class="line">    NSLog(@<span class="string">&quot;Convert Success value is d %d&quot;</span>,value);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    NSLog(@<span class="string">&quot;Convert Fail value is fail %x&quot;</span>,value);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>比较这一下, 你会发现我们都是使用&amp;value,去接收转换后的值.这里不管是什么进制,最终他转换完毕他的本质都是一个数.一个int.</p></blockquote><p>OK! 到这里, 我们已经把我们开始提的两个问题,解决了.<br><strong>那如果要把十六进制字符串转换为八进制的数呢?</strong><br>如果你有点sense,肯定会查阅sscanf和NSScanner的一些详细用法.这两个函数一个是objective c的foundation 函数一个是c语言的库函数.Have a good time哦.</p><p>这里仅仅是提供一种到达罗马的方法,供参考.</p><hr><p>这里主要想表达的是,其实方法不重要,很多时候,搞不清问题的本质,然后就去寻求解决问题的办法到最后,一切都是瞎搞.<br>当我们深刻理解了问题的本质,像这种问题,往往有很多转换的方法.<br>不管什么十六进制,八进制,十进制,也不管什么整形,字符串, 只要理清了,方法就有了.</p><p>这就是为什么往往大厂喜欢找名校CS专业的人作为实习生培养,对他们来说风险小,成本低.</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
